  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Account assistant (Intern)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Assist in data entry of invoices, receipts, and payments</li><li>Support accounts payable and accounts receivable functions</li><li>Help with filing and organizing accounting documents</li><li>Assist in bank reconciliations and expense tracking</li><li>Support month-end closing activities</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc accounting and administrative tasks as assigned</li></ul><p><br /><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Polytechnic diploma or above in Accounting, Finance, Business, or related fields</li><li>Open to interns / fresh graduates</li><li>Basic knowledge of accounting principles</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Excel and Word</li><li>Detail-oriented with good organizational skills</li><li>Willingness to learn and a positive working attitude</li><li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team</li></ul><p><u><strong>Additional Information </strong></u></p><ul><li>Internship duration: (3–6 months)</li><li>Opportunity for full-time conversion based on performance</li></ul>",
